"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔小心獻埋三分比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b623fa4196f542ffc0762897f99f93d2170210","tid":23031,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:33:15.000Z","msg":"我們是表現優秀一方 <br />\n我們應該獲得三分<br />\n我們在鳩斬<br />\n我們在鳩猜<br />\n我們是daddy的巴<br />\n我們本來有機會贏波<br />\n領先一球真好危險<br />\n爵爺你好嗎？<br />\n球證你好嗎？<br />\n我們天天問侯你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f13492cd35295bd7fe95d75470896cfe6630a29","tid":23031,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T17:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}